Package com.g1.mychess.match.dto

Class TournamentPlayerDTO

java.lang.Object
com.g1.mychess.match.dto.TournamentPlayerDTO
public class TournamentPlayerDTO extends Object
Data Transfer Object (DTO) representing a player in a tournament. This class is used to carry information about a player participating in a specific tournament.
